<tr>
<td width="600" colspan="4">
<b>Description</b><br>
This item is dropped by the Kobold King in Lord Nagafen's Lair.  He is surrounded by tons of high level kobolds and will kill even the best of parties if not killed correctly.  He drops the Runed Mithril Bracers as his common loot, and the Fleshripper as his rare.</td>
